short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Automatically sets YouTube videos to the highest quality.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Automatically sets the resolution of a youtube video to the highest setting. Stop youtubes rate limiting from having to set the video to 1080p HD every time, this extension automatically sets the video to HD by auto-clicking the elements on the page for you. Automatically sets to 8k, 4k, 2k, 1080p or whatever the highest available option for a given video is.

All code is available on my github so you can verify this is not malicious
